Description: Native Linux GUI and CLI for OpenVPN 3 Linux
 Production-oriented GTK4/libadwaita desktop GUI and companion CLI for
 OpenVPN 3 Linux. The application integrates with the OpenVPN 3 D-Bus
 services, stores secrets via libsecret, and installs native desktop
 metadata for launcher, MIME, and URI handling.
